{"tid":101534,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［新牌］其實點預自己架車夠唔夠過","createTime":"2017-01-31T02:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T12:16:19.000Z","uid":37856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b526566435cd1411b93e9d08f133529a84fc83fa","tid":101534,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"呢幾日新正頭出車 試過遇到條單線單程路 兩邊都擺滿車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾下真係淆底好驚hi到 最尾都係膽粗粗咁過 其實又夠過<br />\n即係其實除左憑感覺仲有冇咩注意"},{"pid":"c297cb4fb56fc44e47f5740d94c82d39901984ba","tid":101534,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"經驗"},{"pid":"c22653a788aa91f84dc89b76bef7c81a5cbe45ec","tid":101534,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"憑經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2bf2cc05d1d2e465aeb5cd037ef855b5dce599","tid":101534,"uid":57015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"都係感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你車頭尾冇sensors?"},{"pid":"fab44e7baec2a380c45f17ecbf848579f52d374d","tid":101534,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"憑經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但技術唔夠就算點夠過都可能會撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c1a03fd0bc259a074d1e608c04cdfeb2cc526","tid":101534,"uid":67700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"開燈 睇下頭尾燈光照落前車後車既強弱判斷距離"},{"pid":"bdea2ac9bbde81fde2c77fc8f1cb1efd02abc67a","tid":101534,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你車頭尾冇sensors?</blockquote><br />\n我有 所以好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d7b79cc416fd503272e87392ba79bd2cd23535","tid":101534,"uid":19715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"一個字 慢"},{"pid":"4b0608bfed6e1f7a11c25118686ed7f469a8619b","tid":101534,"uid":19738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開燈 睇下頭尾燈光照落前車後車既強弱判斷距離</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由其係啲地獄停車場，睇燈距好有用"},{"pid":"e51e64eda2ba6902feab7b356bf7d38d4acd92a2","tid":101534,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"燈影<br />\n側鏡<br />\n經驗"},{"pid":"250ccf49dbe1a3c1e530c49260f589a2fa47d428","tid":101534,"uid":71213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你車頭尾冇sensors?</blockquote><br />\n我有 所以好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNPR乜撚SENSOR都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44a9b41d4a436cb935ca0f35371c4b1c7d4532a","tid":101534,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"靠感覺<br />\n<br />\n其實你架車駛到兩架車中間之前<br />\n你就可以估到夠唔夠過<br />\n<br />\n估到夠過<br />\n就睇右面倒後鏡<br />\n儘量右鏡貼隔離車<br />\n左面就自然夠過（咁你過之前緊係忘下high唔high到人啦"},{"pid":"ba65aaaa6021141a9a71dd8b4e7df3ae9ff2d0ca","tid":101534,"uid":51705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都係感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你車頭尾冇sensors?</blockquote><br />\n我有 所以好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNPR乜撚SENSOR都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸npr就睇鏡啦，兩邊鏡過到就一定無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3893697b0445dbd2620f360cbb7313f380cfa5","tid":101534,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你車頭尾冇sensors?</blockquote><br />\n倒車屎忽都會響既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1411e20aef84004e4cf5aaec85ac60c7a696a568","tid":101534,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會繼續摸索下"},{"pid":"b71e7ebf415a09e9d8f9e6a79707df2ee54b4a4d","tid":101534,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"出過事就會知<br />\n真心"},{"pid":"06570127788e9441fe614e4c4159c9ae2265e2f1","tid":101534,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"鏡當貓鬚"},{"pid":"4aa56e5bb89861e0847ad0444a9b9de2b04d32a7","tid":101534,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"過完記得報警"},{"pid":"2f78bdac99d5e2df34e0c25844b5c2252b02d7ab","tid":101534,"uid":43381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"睇下前面架車夠唔夠過"},{"pid":"e82619ba91a8e7f9e966fabe5236305fad0839a9","tid":101534,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"跟前面車"},{"pid":"6f8190d2960f3b21cb319e27779cd71b69900b70","tid":101534,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:46:00.000Z","msg":"目測"},{"pid":"9c006866d04d95598267869234ca74cb28729837","tid":101534,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"見聞聲霸